<br>
YES!  A Mage thread!  Imagine....what are the odds...so, for the....(3 is it?) Magi in the Tribe, I hope maybe we can put our racial differences aside for but a moment, and concentrate on visiting the Master....<br>
<br>
Please guys, I wanna bounce a few things off.  First, can I get an idea of whether or not any of the Magi are interested in working on their epic.  I know for damn well sure I am hot to get it, despite the hoops of fire they make me jump through.  <br>
<br>
