<br>
I have actually killed him twice, but no cloak.  <br>
<br>
I am more than happy to help anyone with anything as some of you may have already discovered.  But when it comes to my epic, I am driven.<br>
<br>
Also, I would like to make this thread a place that Magi can sell their spells, or others can sell their Mage spells to us &lt;wink wink&gt;<br>
<br>
Good luck out there Tribe!<br>
<br>
